Installation with Python 2.7.*
1. Install pip
2. Install setuptools module 
   ->sudo pip install --upgrade setuptools
3. Downgrade pip 19.0.3 to pip 9.0.3
   ->sudo pip install --upgrade --force-reinstall pip==9.0.3
4. sudo pip install cfn-lint 
5. Check the instalation 
   ->cfn-lint --version
   
Installation with Python 3.4.*
1. Install pip
2. Install setuptools module 
   ->sudo pip install --upgrade setuptools
3. sudo pip install cfn-lint 
4. Check the instalation 
   ->cfn-lint --version
   
